\c 122 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 122\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Jajuu Yerusaalem (Weedduu ittiin ol ba'an; kan Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* "Gara mana Waaqayyoo dhaqna!" yeroo anaan jedhanitti, ani nan gammade.
\m \bd 2\bd* Ammas miilli keenya, balbaloota kellaa kee keessa in dhaabata, yaa Yerusaalem!
\m \bd 3\bd* Yaa Yerusaalem, ishee mandaraaf akka ta'utti ijaaramtee, ishee tokkummaadhaan walitti hidhamtee.
\m \bd 4\bd* Achitti gosoonni ol in ba'u; gosoota Waaqayyoo ta'anii, Israa'eliif akkuma abboomametti, maqaa Waaqayyoof galata in galchu.
\m \bd 5\bd* Achitti teessoowwan firdii, teessoowwan mana Daawit dhaabamaniiru.
\m \bd 6\bd* Nagaa Yerusaalemiif kadhadhaa! Warri si jaallatan itti tolee gabiitti haa jiraatan!
\m \bd 7\bd* Nagaan masaraa kee keessa, gabiinis mana mootummaa kee keessa haa jiraatu.
\m \bd 8\bd* Sababii obboloota koo fi hiriyoota koof, "Nagaan si keessa haa jiraatu!" nan jedha.
\m \bd 9\bd* Sababii mana Waaqayyoo gooftaa keenyaaf, wanta gaarii argachuu kee nan barbaada!
